            "image_width": 700,
            "title": "Our Role",
            "text": "<p>Reframing the role of the watch from counter of time lost, to a measure of potential opportunity. Inspiring the consideration of what really matters, the things that bring purpose, meaning and joy.<\/p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        },
        "1660914257307c8879-1": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "enable_image": true,
            "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/anders-anne-landscape.jpg",
            "image_width": 700,
            "title": "Our Northstar",
            "text": "<p>Timefulness. Time gives us an opportunity to do more of what matters each and every day. Time is an opportunity that encourages you to be conscious of the choices you make.<\/p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        },
        "1660914257307c8879-2": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "enable_image": true,
            "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/morris-co-beautiful-watch.jpg",
            "image_width": 700,
            "title": "Our Tribe",
            "text": "<p>This is for those who believe we can do more of what matters with the time we have. The ones who find purpose in pursuing the path which brings meaning to their lives.<\/p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        }
